{"tid":2196943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為電訊市場份額在美國制裁下進一步攀升，比愛立信及諾基亞合計更多","createTime":"2020-09-10T09:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T09:17:40.000Z","uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ad747e6761b73b972f52b86f1b576cb932dffbad","tid":2196943,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:17:42.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/216671/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4546%2F216671%2F1%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=b7f2b2cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/216671/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n歐美不少國家紛紛宣佈，不准華為參加 5G 網絡的基建，對於這家中國電訊設備生產商帶來打擊。雖然受到多國抵制，但華為在電訊業的市場份額不但未有縮減，甚至有不跌反升的情況，比起兩大競爭對手 Nokia 和 Ericsson 加起來更多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-09/10/216671/eprice_1_5c3365b64ed6447d057cfa8190208909.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-09%2F10%2F216671%2Feprice_1_5c3365b64ed6447d057cfa8190208909.jpg&h=73758223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據韓國傳媒 The Elec 的報導，華為在電訊市場的佔有率，由 2019 年的 28% 提升到今年上半年的 31%。不過芬蘭電訊設備品牌 Nokia 則由去年的 16%，下跌至今年上半年的 14%；至於瑞典品牌 Ericsson 今年的市場佔有率為 14%，維持與去年不變。華為的市佔率在 2015 年首次超越 Nokia，現時雙方距離進一步擴大。<br />\n<br />\n另一中國電訊設備生產商中興亦有所增長，由去年的 9% 增加至今年第二季的 11%。分析指華為和中興的增長，與中國大力推動 5G 有關，雖然歐美國家傾向使用 Nokia，但當地的 5G 推進速度較慢，而且兩間北歐品牌都無法打入中國 5G 市場，故市佔率有所下降。"},{"pid":"c89d8b0b93bfc763680dadf873ed401bbec3f8ff","tid":2196943,"uid":155095,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jtzb.BWrcWwVtSVcTrQnGw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/centralmarket.tumblr.com/c370935c3f73877c0dfa869f6b79cfe0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fjtzb.BWrcWwVtSVcTrQnGw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fcentralmarket.tumblr.com%2Fc370935c3f73877c0dfa869f6b79cfe0&h=4a8ab8f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2355000/2359346/20190527_HUAWEI2_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2355000%2F2359346%2F20190527_HUAWEI2_1024.png&h=9ec785e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h1DlE9yBybmtRPEasRC4RPGtqbQRiUH1oNQo_dA5SMF8oXCg9ZF8lXn1pMForBSk1OFklDnE6dVovWXs_Olgl/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0h1DlE9yBybmtRPEasRC4RPGtqbQRiUH1oNQo_dA5SMF8oXCg9ZF8lXn1pMForBSk1OFklDnE6dVovWXs_Olgl%2Fw644&h=b439e548&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eea65e2f50bd940f95bf654b1317028e9ce52eff","tid":2196943,"uid":193642,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"而且兩間北歐品牌都無法<ins>打入</ins>中國 5G 市場 (X)<br />\n而且兩間北歐品牌都無法<span class=\"xx-large\">進入</span>中國 5G 市場 (V)"},{"pid":"9daa24d3b43d8d55efd69ef8825d71858ece6596","tid":2196943,"uid":14918,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:34:10.000Z","msg":"所謂市場份額計埋支那果份就真係唔準啦"},{"pid":"cd6028a0bc465fbb5df73fafb4fbbb23280bb08c","tid":2196943,"uid":108213,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:35:09.000Z","msg":"識自慰咪好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297e82853c0e12a5c6e3e8c6461347aaa7ddb2c9","tid":2196943,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T11:00:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96f9ca4497973f43247685caee05c52e6af62f54","tid":2196943,"uid":290750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"終極打炮！！"},{"pid":"1ab02544ec46835aac3e0ef848f7e1c4f3c70a66","tid":2196943,"uid":290750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci